How to Request Account Deletion
To delete your account:

Open the Recipe Planner app.

Go to Home > Menu > Your account > Delete Account

Follow the on-screen prompts to confirm your request.

Alternatively, you may contact us at pandapanda94@comcast.net with the subject line: "Account Deletion Request", and include the email address associated with your account.

What Data Will Be Deleted
Upon account deletion, we will permanently remove the following data:

Your profile information (name, email)

Any content you have created or uploaded

For more information, please refer to our Privacy Policy or contact us at pandapanda94@comcast.net
